Assistant Telebot is a Google Chrome™ extension from AICALLS that make you call any phone number straight from where you are on a webpage. You’ll save valuable time on each call, and what’s more, you won’t miss any inbound call from your customers. 

Once you install the Assistant Telebot by AICALLS, you can click a phone number, and the call is placed through our Assistant Telebot. And what’s more, when customers call in by the number you call out, the smart system will show you the inbound call number, and you can choose to pick it up, and Answer the call.

It’s a great way to save your time and keep your customers trusting you :

*  Call any number in your web browser with one click.
*  Save time per call and improve your calling accuracy.
*  Don’t miss any inbound call from your customers.
*  Large spreadsheet of numbers to call? Copy it to Google Sheets, and make a clickable dialing directory.
